e $29.95.andM;Centa Systems is at 5130 E. La Palma Ave., Suite 106, Anaheim, Calif.andP;  92807.andO;Phone (714) 693-8825 or (800) 522-5939, Ext.andP;  470; fax (714) 693-8618.andO;</TEXT></DOC>